BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Performance,Lecture/Presentation/Talk
DESCRIPTION:How RADWIMPS Satoshi Yamaguchi Reclaimed Music Through Neurosci
 ence Research and Voice-Controlled Drums.\n\nThis lecture-performance focus
 es on the life lessons Satoshi Yamaguchi has learned through major turning 
 points marked by both success and setback as a professional musician. Drawi
 ng on his personal journey\, the talk explores how music\, research\, and t
 echnology became interconnected\, leading to the emergence of new forms of 
 creative expression.\n\nSatoshi will also be joined by special guests Roy a
 nd PJ Hirabayashi and performers from Stanford Taiko for a special collabor
 ation! \n\nAdmission Information\n\nFree admissionPlease RSVP here!
DTEND:20260209T050000Z
DTSTAMP:20260308T083906Z
