  and use it to explore simple data sets.\n\nAt the end of this class\, part
 icipants will be able to:\n\n Articulate and identify the basic syntax of R
 .  Understand the key principles of vectorization.  Identify and use the ba
 sic data structures provided in R.\n\nThis class is in person\, please brin
 g your own laptop. If you are planning to attend Part 2 (next week)\, make 
 sure you register for each class separately.\n\nAccreditation Statement\nIn
