CATEGORIES:Social Event/Reception
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a K-Pop data extravaganza! Join us during Love Da
 ta Week 2026 for an immersive\, interactive event that combines your love o
 f K-Pop with the power of data. Whether you're a die-hard K-Pop fan or just
  curious about the global phenomenon\, this fun\, hands-on experience will 
 reveal how data is shaping the music industry's hottest trends.\n\n As a K-
 Pop Data Hunter\, you'll embark on a journey to uncover the stories behind 
 the music. Explore curated resources from Stanford's K-Pop collection\, fea
 turing over 150 Korean titles\, CDs\, and posters. You'll learn how data is
  collected\, analyzed\, and shared to understand the K-Pop universe from so
 ng metrics to fan engagement. Plus\, participate in exciting activities\, i
 ncluding an OX quiz\, Guess the Song challenge\, and Bingo\, with prizes to
  be won! \n\nThis event will take place in the courtyard outside the East A
 sia Library.\n\nWe will be taking photos at this event for publicity purpos
 es. Your presence at this event constitutes consent to be photographed unle
 ss you express otherwise.
