CATEGORIES:Lecture/Presentation/Talk
DESCRIPTION:A heart failure diagnosis doesn’t mean stopping the activities 
 you love. Join Eldrin Lewis\, MD\, MPH\, as he outlines modern approaches t
 o care from initial diagnostic workup to the Four Pillars of therapy—the fo
 undational medications for heart failure. Dr. Lewis will share essential st
 rategies for integrating quality of life into your care plan\, empowering y
 ou to work with your doctor to prioritize your well-being and independence.
 \n\nThis webinar will be presented by Eldrin Lewis\, MD\, MPH\, who is Chie
 f of the Division of Cardiovascular Medicine and a professor at Stanford Un
 iversity School of Medicine. He is an internationally recognized expert in 
 advanced heart failure\, heart transplant\, and improving quality of life f
 or heart failure patients. As of 2024\, he serves as president of the Weste
 rn States Board of the American Heart Association\, helping steer regional 
 efforts in prevention\, health equity\, and community outreach.
