BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Lecture/Presentation/Talk
DESCRIPTION:The Global Sustainability Challenge is an ambitious new initiat
 ive led by the Stanford Doerr School of Sustainability in collaboration wit
 h leading universities around the world\, including including Technical Uni
 versity of Munich\, IIT Bombay\, The Hong Kong University of Science & Tech
 nology\, Zhejiang University\, Imperial College London\, and more. Our miss
 ion is to create a global platform to mobilize college students worldwide t
 o develop real-world sustainability solutions for their communities. \n\nWe
  are pleased to host the Americas Finals on Feb. 13\, where finalist teams 
 from North and South America will showcase their work. Watch the livestream
  for key moments from the Americas Finals. \n\nOpening remarks: https://www
 .youtube.com/live/klDyGt_Fqww?si=quujxcsE8Y_dEPhm\n\n8:00 a.m. – 8:15 a.m. 
