 ng territory\, both infrastructurally and diplomatically\, would form the b
 asis of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization.\n\nShe is a Research Associ
 ate at The Arctic Institute and a Research Fellow with the North American a
 nd Arctic Defense and Security Network. She has published a book chapter on
