DESCRIPTION:Welcome to QTrees\, a supportive and inclusive space designed s
 pecifically for queer Stanford students navigating their unique journeys.\n
 \nThis group during Winter quarter provides a safe\, affirming environment 
 where members can explore their LGBTQ+ identities\, share experiences\, and
  find solidarity with others who understand their struggles and triumphs.\n
 \nQTrees will meet for 60 mins\, weekly for 5 weeks\, with the same people 
 each week.Facilitated by Christine Catipon\, PsyDAll enrolled students are 
 eligible to participate in CAPS groups and workshops.Meeting with a facilit
 ator is required to join this group. You can sign up on the INTEREST LIST_Q
 Trees_IN-PERSON_WINTER_Q on Vaden Portal rosters\, in the "Groups and Works
 hops" section. The location of the group will be provided upon completion o
 f the pre-group meeting with the facilitator.
