 pora? What is it like to teach Jewish Studies\, Yiddish language\, and anti
 semitism at a Chinese University? Join Meng Yang\, Assistant Professor at P
 eking University in conversation with Stanford Professor of Anthropology\, 
 Matthew Kohrman\, to explore these questions.\n\nThis event is co-sponsored
  with the Center for East Asian Studies\, the Center for Comparative Studie
 s in Race and Ethnicity\, and the Department of Anthropology.
