BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Class/Seminar
DESCRIPTION:Nurturing Africa’s AI Leaders through Math Olympiad\n\nHAI & SD
 S Seminar with Gaidi Faraj\, Lofred Madzou\, Sanmi Koyejo\, Ravi Vakil\n\nV
 isit our website to learn more about the event agenda\, speakers\, and othe
 r details\n\nThe African Olympiad Academy is a world-class high school dedi
 cated to training Africa’s most promising students in mathematics\, science
 \, and artificial intelligence through olympiad-based pedagogy. Olympiads a
 re globally recognized competitions for top high-school students that empha
 size deep inquiry and rigorous problem solving.\n\nThere is growing evidenc
 e that olympiad education is a powerful pipeline for exceptional AI talent.
  Notable olympiad alumni include Mira Murati (former CTO of OpenAI)\, Alexa
 ndr Wang (CEO of Scale AI)\, and Aravind Srinivas (CEO of Perplexity AI)\, 
 among many others.\n\nIn this seminar\, AOA Founders will discuss their app
 roach to identifying and developing top-tier AI talent on the African conti
 nent in coordination with complementary initiatives such as Black in AI. Th
 e conversation will highlight how strategic investments in olympiad program
 s can unlock Africa’s vast potential as a global hub for AI talent.
DTEND:20260225T211500Z
DTSTAMP:20260308T083908Z
DTSTART:20260225T200000Z
