CATEGORIES:Meeting
DESCRIPTION:We’re excited to invite you to our Advising Meet & Greet Series
 !\n\nJoin us on Friday\, February 27th from 12:00–2:00 PM in Y2E2 131 to co
 nnect with faculty and meet potential major advisors in a relaxed\, informa
 l setting.\n\nFaculty in attendance include:\nTadashi Fukami\nScott Fendorf
 \nSteve Davis\nAnthony Kovscek\n\nThis is a great opportunity to ask questi
 ons\, explore research interests\, and build relationships with professors 
 you may be considering as your major advisor.\n\n🍕 Pizza will be provided f
 rom Pizza My Heart\nTo help us create a more sustainable event\, please RSV
