BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Other
DESCRIPTION:Did you know that advisors from Fidelity Investments and TIAA p
 rovide free individual financial counseling on campus at your convenience? 
 They can offer guidance on the best strategy to meet your retirement goals 
 through Stanford's retirement savings plans.\n\nContact Fidelity directly t
 o schedule an appointment with a representative to review your current and 
 future retirement savings options:\n\nFidelity appointment scheduler(800) 6
 42-7131
