DESCRIPTION:Register Here\n\nTrying to choose a major? Interested in both t
 echnology and the humanities? Curious about what Science\, Technology\, and
  Society (STS) is all about?\n\nMaybe you’re wondering how to combine inter
 ests like biology and history\, communications and design\, or even electri
 cal engineering and public policy. Or perhaps you want to know what you can
  do with an STS degree beyond Stanford.\n\nJoin us (and enjoy some great fo
 od!) at the STS Prospective Majors Dinner\, where we’ll answer all these qu
 estions and more.\n\nThe dinner will take place on Wednesday\, March 4\, 20
 26\, from 5:15–6:30 PM in the courtyard in front of Wilbur Dining Hall. Fee
 l free to stop by at any time during the event!
