DESCRIPTION:Mark your calendar for an unforgettable day of inspiration\, br
 eakthrough learning\, and transformative connections at the 2026 Women's Le
 adership Summit.\n\nThis year\, we are honored to welcome Yvonne (Bonnie) M
 aldonado\, MD\, as our keynote speaker. Recently appointed Vice Provost for
  Faculty Advancement\, Bonnie is a global leader in infectious disease rese
 arch\, vaccine development\, and public health impact.\n\nIn addition to ou
 r keynote speaker\, the day will include engaging presentations and panel d
 iscussions with innovators and thought leaders\, workshops on timely topics
  to drive meaningful change\, and networking opportunities to connect with 
 inspiring professionals.\n\nThe program topics will include:\n\nDiscovering
  Your Potential: Lessons Learned Along Our Leadership JourneysNegotiation: 
 Getting (More of) What You WantLeadership in Difficult TimesArt and Wellnes
 sThe Power of Collaboration in LeadershipCreation\, Collaboration\, and Com
 municationEmpowering the InvestorCultivating ExcellenceAnd More!\n Registra
 tion:\n\nEarly Bird Admission $425.00 (available through February 3\, 2026)
 \nGeneral Admission $475.00 (available February 4 - February 27\, 2026\, or
  until tickets sell out)\n\nRegistration includes access to all sessions\, 
 continental breakfast\, lunch and closing reception.\n\nThe registration fo
 rm includes an opportunity to request accommodations for disabilities and f
 or dietary restrictions and allergies.
