  group will focus on providing mutual support\, sharing wisdom\, increasing
  self-compassion\, and enhancing overall coping and wellness.\n\nMeeting wi
 th a facilitator is required to join this group. You can sign up on the INT
 EREST LIST_LIVING_WITH_OCD_IN-PERSON_WINTER_Q on Vaden Portal rosters\, in 
