 e’ll cover material from Elements of Academic Style\, and focus on two part
 icular areas of interest: the Uneven U\, and how to produce dynamic amplitu
 de in your writing.\n\nThe session will begin with a 30-minute talk\, follo
 wed by a 15-minute exercise\, and will conclude with time for questions and
  conversation. \n\nRSVP for writing workshop with Prof. Eric Hayot
