DESCRIPTION:Hear the remarkable story of Omer Shem Tov\, who survived 505 d
 ays in Hamas captivity after being abducted during the October 7th Terroris
 t Attack. His journey of resilience\, faith\, and courage has made his voic
 e essential in raising awareness and advocating for the safe return of all 
 hostages and Jewish people around the world. Join us for an inspiring eveni
 ng and a rare opportunity for the Stanford community to connect with a powe
 rful story of survival\, strength\, and hope.
