CATEGORIES:Religious/Spiritual
DESCRIPTION:Season of Lent: Lent is the forty-day period (excluding Sundays
 ) of prayer\, repentance and self-denial that precedes Easter.\n\nUniversit
 y Public Worship gathers weekly for the religious\, spiritual\, ethical\, a
 nd moral formation of the Stanford community. Rooted in the history and pro
 gressive Christian tradition of Stanford’s historic Memorial Church\, we cu
 ltivate a community of compassion and belonging through ecumenical Christia
 n worship and occasional multifaith celebrations.
