BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Class/Seminar
DESCRIPTION:Planning for retirement can feel overwhelming\, especially if y
 ou are unsure how your retirement plan works or whether you are saving enou
 gh. With so many options\, rules\, and financial priorities competing for y
 our attention\, it can be easy to put retirement planning off for another d
 ay. However\, taking even small steps now can make a meaningful difference 
 for your future financial security.\n\nIn this free webinar\, you will lear
 n the fundamentals of understanding your retirement plan and the steps need
 ed to enroll. We will walk through how to evaluate whether you are on track
  with your savings and explore practical ways to increase your contribution
 s over time\, even if you are starting later or saving on a limited budget.
 \n\nWhether you are just beginning your retirement journey or want reassura
 nce that you are making the most of your current plan\, you will leave with
  greater confidence\, clearer next steps\, and tools to help you start savi
 ng for the future you envision.\n\nThis class will not be recorded. Attenda
 nce requirement for incentive points - at least 80% of the live session.  R
 equest disability accommodations and access info.\n\nClass details are subj
 ect to change.
DTEND:20260407T200000Z
