DESCRIPTION:The first Monday of each month\, the Knight Initiative for Brai
 n Resilience will host monthly seminars to bring together awardees\, affili
 ated professors and students for a series of 'lab meeting' styled talks. Tw
 o speakers will discuss their brain resilience research\, experiences in th
 e field\, and answer questions about their work.\n\nTo support our research
 ers' participation in this open science ‘lab-meeting style’ exchange of ide
 as\, these seminars are not streamed/recorded and are only open to members 
 of the Stanford community. \n\nCaitlin Taylor\, Stanford University\n\nTalk
  title TBD\n\nLay research TBD\n\n \n\nGaurav Chattree \, Stanford Universi
 ty\n\nTalk title TBD\n\nLay research TBD\n\n \n\n \n\nEVENT POSTER COMING S
 OON
