 nce\; insights from computational and theoretical neuroscience\; and the de
 velopment of novel research technologies and neuro-engineering breakthrough
 s.\n\nUnless otherwise noted\, seminars are held Thursdays at 12:00 noon PT
 .\n\nSign up to learn about all our upcoming events
