 o be recognized for making figurative sculpture modern by redefining the ex
 pressive capacity of the human form. IMAGE: Auguste Rodin (France\, 1840–19
 17)\, The Age of Bronze (L’Âge d’airain)\, 1875-1876. Bronze\, cast c. 1920
 . Gift of the B. Gerald Cantor Collection\, 1983.300\n\nPublic Tours: Frida
 ys and Saturdays at 11:30am\n\nAdmission Info\n\nTours do not require a res
 ervation and are free of charge.\n\nFirst come\, first served!
