BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Lecture/Presentation/Talk
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for this month's Center for Sleep and Circadian 
 Sciences William C. Dement Seminar Series!\n\n"Metabolic Drivers of Sleep D
 isruption in Alzheimer’s Disease"\n\nFriday\, May 15th\, 2026 at 12pm PST\n
 \nShannon L. Macauley\, Ph.D.\nAssociate Professor\, Dept of Physiology\, U
