DESCRIPTION:Dr. Sarita Patel\, Board-Certified Child and Adolescent Psychia
 trist\, will discuss the many factors beyond ADHD that can affect a young c
 hild’s ability to focus\, including: anxiety\, developmental delays\, senso
 ry sensitivities\, sleep issues\, and temperament. Designed to inform and e
 mpower without pressuring families to self-diagnose\, this session offers a
  compassionate look at the complexities behind attention difficulties in yo
 ung children.\n\nThis workshop is geared towards parents of children in ele
 mentary school\, though all are welcome to attend. This session will not be
  recorded.
