 he speaker for one of these enriching experiences.\n\nSpeaker Meet-ups Inte
 rest Form\n\n About the Wu Tsai Neurosciences Seminar SeriesThe Wu Tsai Neu
 rosciences Institute seminar series brings together the Stanford neuroscien
 ce community to discuss cutting-edge\, cross-disciplinary brain research\, 
 from biochemistry to behavior and beyond.\n\nTopics include new discoveries
  in fundamental neurobiology\; advances in human and translational neurosci
 ence\; insights from computational and theoretical neuroscience\; and the d
 evelopment of novel research technologies and neuro-engineering breakthroug
 hs.\n\nUnless otherwise noted\, seminars are held Thursdays at 12:00 noon P
 T.\n\nSign up to learn about all our upcoming events
