DESCRIPTION:Ecumenical Christian Service with Rev. Glen Davis\, Chaplain Af
 filiate\, Preaching.\n\n \n\nUniversity Public Worship gathers weekly for t
 he religious\, spiritual\, ethical\, and moral formation of the Stanford co
 mmunity. Rooted in the history and progressive Christian tradition of Stanf
 ord’s historic Memorial Church\, we cultivate a community of compassion and
  belonging through ecumenical Christian worship and occasional multifaith c
 elebrations. \n\nDoors open at 10:30 am.
